data.description:
Beautiful pristine Golf Course home in Lost Plantation. Experience ‘almost new construction’ (c. 2018) in
this amenity filled neighborhood – golf course, pool, tennis, playgrounds, etc with Top-Rated Schools!
This open concept home has numerous features and upgrades. A formal Living or Dining space, Granite
and S.S. in the Kitchen w/ island & bar overlooking the Entertaining Great Rm area. Mudrm / Drop Zone and large Guest Rm downstairs. Light filled interior space throughout - all with sweeping views of the
Golf Course and private outdoor patio. Over-scaled Master Suite up (dual closets, sitting area, deluxe
bath area) as well as additional Bdrms. Numerous details: tray ceilings, spray insulation, water filtration
system, etc…. A superb choice in a superb location!!
